            "raw_text": "1\n\nWeisstein, Eric W. \"Poisson Distribution.\"\nFrom MathWorld--A Wolfram Web Resource.\nhttps://mathworld.wolfram.com/PoissonDistribution.html",
            "type": "raw_block"
